  {% bubble HiMERU %}
    —"Werewolf"?
  {% endbubble %}

  {% bubble Rinne %}
    Thaaaat's right. It's a game where you gotta pick out the lying wereworlf among your friends by talking to them.<sup>**(1)**</sup>

