  {% endbubble %}

  {% bubble Kohaku %}
    Hmph!
  {% endbubble %}

  {% bubble Rinne %}
    Rinne-kun says some wise things sometimes, right? Whenever that happens I can't help but think he's got some sort of doppelgänger or something.
  {% endbubble %}

